  "detailed_description": "Aim for the \"peak\" of the freak world with a card game! FREE.KS PEAK, a trading card game full of freaks.<br>Defeat enemies and acquire cards. Build your deck with the cards you get and become the best card player!<br><br>————————————————————————————————————————————————<br><br>This is a world where non-human \"Free.ks\" gather.<br>It is ruled by a powerful emperor named Dorotea, and the Free.ks compete for strength in a card game called \"Peak\".<br>As kings who rule their respective lands, there are Yueping, Cleao, Cheche, Mary, Frank, Neruru, and Camille. To fulfill their ambitions, they aim for even greater heights in \"Peak\"ー<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/e95ae976d55a216980ca49348f8770a5.poster.avif?t=1758775171\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/e95ae976d55a216980ca49348f8770a5.webm?t=1758775171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/e95ae976d55a216980ca49348f8770a5.mp4?t=1758775171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/8787d80812ffd7d3fc69f36caab15c11.poster.avif?t=1758775171\" width=620 height=349 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/8787d80812ffd7d3fc69f36caab15c11.webm?t=1758775171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>[Unique Characters]</strong><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/5dc9ff81b257294d0ea2af2611063c18.avif?t=1758775171\" width=620 height=349 /></span><br>The characters are all eccentric freaks, such as the gourmand Kyonshi, the free-spirited black cat, and the artificial human with multiple personalities. Defeat the enemies that stand in your way with \"PEAK\" and aim for the top!<br><br><strong>【🐲💐 Choose Freely from 9 Freaks】</strong><br>Each freak has a powerful unique card!<br>Choose which of the 9 greedy monsters to command and decide what strategy you'll use!\t\t\t<br>🐈‍⬛Cheche, a mischievous black cat demon who loves to control humans as he pleases.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/2417f112725a0116e178775c6999f563.avif?t=1758775171\" width=620 height=268 /></span><br><br>🧛Moriko, a vampire who loves money and aims to become the strongest to become rich.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/9f59c41da7edc1cf9a5b38d8a211e03d.avif?t=1758775171\" width=620 height=268 /></span><br><br>🐍Emperor Dorothea, who rules in the name of God.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/5e882243e2ac6220404e7d1dd9eea1ee.avif?t=1758775171\" width=620 height=268 /></span><br><br>🐺Camille, a werewolf who aims to become the strongest in pursuit of his ideal self.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/394019cda8c75eeb25bd078d3da98949.avif?t=1758775171\" width=620 height=268 /></span><br><br>👻Neruru, a phantom who wants to become an idol and win everyone's hearts.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/0776d152f1258fd46a8ea67da338f721.avif?t=1758775171\" width=620 height=268 /></span><br><br>🤖Frank, a human-made being who combined with five others to become the strongest.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/0f8a32c097b15f3545060130eec8ffcf.avif?t=1758775171\" width=620 height=268 /></span><br><br>🏜️Queen Cleo, who believes in authority and is ruled by law.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/a88198d0a18ee7f3ad40cfc185f8dcdc.avif?t=1758775171\" width=620 height=268 /></span><br><br>🍜Yuepin, a Jiangshi (hopping vampire) who seeks to become the strongest to devour freaks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/91aba65d1763b906698a9059b8c5ce2f.avif?t=1758775171\" width=620 height=268 /></span><br><br>🐑Merry, a skeleton sheep who lives for love.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/e86352d3cc55c00d9e6b176e6f4ad8a1.avif?t=1758775171\" width=620 height=268 /></span>\t\t<br><br><strong>[Story Mode]</strong><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/1125c497d1f93f0dc7358072cb65776d.avif?t=1758775171\" width=620 height=349 /></span><br>Enjoy the lively story of these unique Free.ks!<br><br><strong>[Rate Battle]</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/51a62c5d3c7758b6c604779264ea0281.avif?t=1758775171\" width=620 height=349 /></span><br>Defeat your enemies, earn points, and aim for first place!<br><br><strong>[Free Battle]</strong><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/37b0c745c4f4e66e713d4b5760cf6127.avif?t=1758775171\" width=620 height=349 /></span><br>Play against any deck, any opponent, and any settings you like!<br><br><strong>[Edit Deck]</strong><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457730/extras/263ec17f5e75d8be54849e81f24668ae.avif?t=1758775171\" width=620 height=349 /></span><br>Edit card decks. Build your own deck with your favorite cards!",
